{"ID":"20250521183558-ee480po","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"custom-sy-fullwidth":"true","id":"20250521183558-ee480po","title":"高压互锁","type":"doc","updated":"20250708130336"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250521183558-7j8zp2r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250521183558-7j8zp2r","updated":"20250521183603"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"CCU共涉及5路互锁：外部互锁检测CCU-EAC、CCU-WPTC、CCU-PDU；自身互锁检测CCU-AC口、CCU-DC口（当互锁断开超3S以上，CCU上报互锁故障）。"}]},{"ID":"20250708130336-n4775e4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250708130336-n4775e4","updated":"20250708130336"}}]}